     SHURGET HOMEPAGE — views/index.ejs
     Sections:
       1. Hero
       2. Trust bar
       3. Problem / stats (the "last mile" pain)
       4. How it works
       5. Driver section
       6. Business / partner section
       7. Final CTA
     ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<!-- ── 1. HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">On-Demand · Same Day · Your City</div>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">The Truck<br>Comes to You.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Furniture, appliances, marketplace finds — booked in 60 seconds, delivered today by a vetted local driver in a pickup truck.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/book" class="btn-hero-primary">Book a Haul Now →</a>
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-hero-ghost">See How It Works</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-proof">
      <span>✓ No subscription</span>
      <span>✓ Instant quote</span>
      <span>✓ Real-time tracking</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll-hint">
    <span>↓</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── 2. TRUST BAR ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="trust-bar">
  <div class="trust-inner">
    <div class="trust-item">
      <div class="trust-num">60s</div>
      <div class="trust-label">Average booking time</div>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-divider"></div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <div class="trust-num">Same Day</div>
      <div class="trust-label">Delivery available</div>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-divider"></div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <div class="trust-num">$49+</div>
      <div class="trust-label">Flat-rate pricing</div>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-divider"></div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <div class="trust-num">100%</div>
      <div class="trust-label">Vetted local drivers</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── 3. THE PROBLEM / STATS ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="problem-section" id="problem">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label">The Last Mile Problem</div>
    <h2 class="section-headline">You Found the Perfect Piece.<br>Now What?</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Millions of purchases stall at the finish line every day — not because the item is wrong, but because getting it home is too hard, too expensive, or too slow.</p>

    <div class="stat-grid">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-icon">🛋️</div>
        <div class="stat-value">1 in 3</div>
        <div class="stat-desc">furniture purchases are abandoned or delayed because the buyer has no way to transport it home.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-icon">💸</div>
        <div class="stat-value">$200–$500</div>
        <div class="stat-desc">is what traditional moving companies charge for a single large-item delivery — often with a 2-week wait.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-icon">📦</div>
        <div class="stat-value">62%</div>
        <div class="stat-desc">of marketplace buyers say "no delivery option" is their #1 reason for not completing a purchase.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-icon">⏱️</div>
        <div class="stat-value">Today</div>
        <div class="stat-desc">Shurget delivers in hours, not days — at a fraction of the cost of traditional delivery services.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-callout">
      <div class="callout-text">
        <h3>The gap between "I want it" and "I have it" costs buyers money, time, and frustration.</h3>
        <p>Shurget closes that gap. A vetted local driver with a pickup truck shows up, loads your item, and delivers it — today.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/book" class="btn-primary">Book Your Haul →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── 4. HOW IT WORKS ────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="how-section" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label">Simple by Design</div>
    <h2 class="section-headline">Three Steps.<br>Done.</h2>

    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">01</div>
        <div class="step-icon">📍</div>
        <h3>Tell Us What & Where</h3>
        <p>Enter your pickup and drop-off addresses, select your item type, and get an instant flat-rate quote. No surprises.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-connector">→</div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">02</div>
        <div class="step-icon">💳</div>
        <h3>Pay Securely</h3>
        <p>Checkout takes 30 seconds via Stripe. Your card is only charged once your driver confirms the job.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-connector">→</div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-number">03</div>
        <div class="step-icon">🚛</div>
        <h3>Your Driver Arrives</h3>
        <p>A local vetted driver with a pickup truck arrives at the scheduled time, loads your item, and delivers it to your door.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="items-section">
      <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">We haul anything that fits in a truck bed</div>
      <div class="items-grid">
        <div class="item-chip">🛋️ Furniture</div>
        <div class="item-chip">🛏️ Mattresses</div>
        <div class="item-chip">🧺 Appliances</div>
        <div class="item-chip">🏗️ Building Materials</div>
        <div class="item-chip">🌿 Landscaping</div>
        <div class="item-chip">📦 Moving Boxes</div>
        <div class="item-chip">🛒 Marketplace Pickups</div>
        <div class="item-chip">🛍️ Retail Runs</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── 5. DRIVER SECTION ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="driver-section" id="drivers">
  <div class="driver-inner">
    <div class="driver-text">
      <div class="section-label light">For Drivers</div>
      <h2 class="section-headline light">Your Truck<br>Is an Asset.<br>Start Using It.</h2>
      <p class="driver-sub">If you own a pickup truck, you're sitting on an income source you haven't tapped yet. Shurget connects you with customers who need exactly what you have — today, on your schedule.</p>

      <div class="driver-perks">
        <div class="perk">
          <div class="perk-icon">💰</div>
          <div class="perk-text">
            <strong>$50–$150 per job</strong>
            <span>Keep the lion's share of every fare. No rental fees, no vehicle costs — just your truck and your time.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="perk">
          <div class="perk-icon">🗓️</div>
          <div class="perk-text">
            <strong>You set the schedule</strong>
            <span>Pick up jobs when it works for you. Accept a haul on a Saturday morning or squeeze one in after work. No shifts, no boss.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="perk">
          <div class="perk-icon">👆</div>
          <div class="perk-text">
            <strong>You choose every job</strong>
            <span>Review the pickup location, drop-off, item type, and payout before accepting. Never take a job you don't want.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="perk">
          <div class="perk-icon">⚡</div>
          <div class="perk-text">
            <strong>Same-day payouts</strong>
            <span>Earnings transfer directly to your bank via Stripe. No waiting weeks for a check.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/drive" class="btn-driver">Apply to Drive — It's Free →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="driver-earnings-card">
      <div class="earnings-label">Driver Earnings Estimate</div>
      <div class="earnings-scenario">
        <div class="scenario-name">Weekend Warrior</div>
        <div class="scenario-desc">4 jobs on Saturday + Sunday</div>
        <div class="scenario-amount">$280 – $480</div>
        <div class="scenario-note">per weekend</div>
      </div>
      <div class="earnings-divider"></div>
      <div class="earnings-scenario">
        <div class="scenario-name">Part-Time Driver</div>
        <div class="scenario-desc">10–12 jobs per week</div>
        <div class="scenario-amount">$700 – $1,200</div>
        <div class="scenario-note">per week</div>
      </div>
      <div class="earnings-divider"></div>
      <div class="earnings-scenario">
        <div class="scenario-name">Full-Time Hauler</div>
        <div class="scenario-desc">20–25 jobs per week</div>
        <div class="scenario-amount">$1,400 – $2,800</div>
        <div class="scenario-note">per week</div>
      </div>
      <div class="earnings-disclaimer">Estimates based on average job payouts. Actual earnings vary by market and availability.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── 6. BUSINESS / PARTNER SECTION ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="business-section" id="business">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label">For Small Businesses</div>
    <h2 class="section-headline">Stop Losing Sales<br>at the Finish Line.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">If your customers can't get their purchase home, they don't buy. It's that simple. Shurget gives your business an on-demand delivery option without hiring a driver, buying a truck, or building any infrastructure.</p>

    <div class="business-grid">
      <div class="business-card">
        <div class="business-icon">📉</div>
        <h3>The Sales You're Losing</h3>
        <p>Furniture stores, appliance dealers, hardware stores, and home goods retailers lose 20–40% of potential sales because customers walk away when delivery is too expensive, too slow, or simply unavailable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="business-card">
        <div class="business-icon">🤝</div>
        <h3>The Shurget Partnership</h3>
        <p>Join our pilot program and offer same-day on-demand truck delivery to your customers at the point of sale. We handle the driver, the booking, the logistics, and the payment — you just close more deals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="business-card highlight-card">
        <div class="business-icon">💵</div>
        <h3>Pilot Program Incentives</h3>
        <p>Early business partners retain an exceptionally large share of the delivery transaction value. As a founding partner, your business earns meaningful revenue on every haul booked through your storefront — turning delivery from a cost center into a revenue stream.</p>
        <a href="/partners" class="btn-business">Learn About Partnership →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="business-logos-label">Ideal for businesses like these</div>
    <div class="business-types">
      <div class="biz-type">🛋️ Furniture Stores</div>
      <div class="biz-type">🧺 Appliance Dealers</div>
      <div class="biz-type">🏗️ Hardware & Lumber</div>
      <div class="biz-type">🌿 Garden Centers</div>
      <div class="biz-type">🖼️ Antique Shops</div>
      <div class="biz-type">🏠 Estate Sales</div>
      <div class="biz-type">📦 Moving Suppliers</div>
      <div class="biz-type">🎨 Home Décor</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── 7. FINAL CTA ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="final-cta">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <h2 class="cta-headline">Ready to Move?</h2>
    <p class="cta-sub">Book in 60 seconds. A driver is standing by.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="/book" class="btn-hero-primary">Book a Haul Now →</a>
      <a href="/drive" class="btn-hero-ghost">Become a Driver</a>
      <a href="/partners" class="btn-hero-ghost">Partner With Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

